>>---------------------------------
>>-- DEFINE TRIGGER btrigA
>>---------------------------------
>>
>>CREATE TRIGGER btrigA
+>BEFORE UPDATE OF (b) 
+>ON tab1A
+>REFERENCING NEW AS newR, OLD AS oldR FOR EACH ROW
+>WHEN (newR.b = oldR.b +1)
+>SET newR.b = oldR.b +2;

--- SQL operation complete.
>>
